  "texts": [
    "However, the query \"AI+hallucination\" yielded only 3 papers.",
    "Conversely, within the Scopus database, searches for \"AI hallucination\" or \"AI+hallucination\" resulted in a total of 1445 records across all fields over the same 10-year period.",
    "To manage this extensive dataset, we refined our search criteria to focus on the Title, Abstract, or Introduction, which reduced the results to 483 relevant records.",
    "A detailed review of each abstract led us to download papers that appeared pertinent to AI hallucination.",
    "This approach significantly differed from searching within abstracts alone, which produced only 49 records and missed some relevant documents.In PubMed Central (PMC), the query \"AI+hallucination\" yielded just 1 paper."
